	"stage.reloaded": "休息室",
	"stage.reloaded.description": "這場景⋯⋯是鹹片的拍攝現場吧？恭喜你，答對了，攝影機還正轉著呢。",
	// Shitfucks Café: Named Shitfucks. The exact coffee shop that Chester works at. Sells coffee that inflates people, and agreed
